Tooltip.zhCN:
我们是艾尔的利刃
强大的近战战士。可以使用震慑冲锋技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
We are the Blades of El
Powerful melee warriors. Can use the stunning charge skill.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
我们只是虚空中的乱影
先进远程步战机甲。可以使用相位闪现和隐匿力场技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
We are just shadows in the void
Advanced long-range infantry combat mecha. Can use Phase Blink and Invisibility Field skills.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
先进机械支援单位。可以使用护盾充能、相位力场和守护者之盾技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Advanced mechanical support unit. Can use Shield Charge, Phase Field, and Guardian Shield abilities.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
达拉姆万岁
远程特种单位。可以使用灵能投影和引导轨道打击技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Long live Durham
Long-range special unit. Can use psionic projection and guided orbital strike skills.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
圣堂武士的力量无人可挡
非常强大的近战战士。可以使用荣耀冲锋、旋风斩和护盾储能器技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
The Templar's power is unstoppable
A very powerful melee fighter. Can use the Glory Charge, Whirlwind and Shield Charger skills.

Can target the ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
我已回归
先进强化远程步战机甲。可以使用风暴迫击技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
I have returned
Advanced and enhanced long-range infantry combat mecha. Can use storm mortar skill.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
我们的命运和家园同在
致命的近战杀手，永久隐形。能够使用闪现、潜行和引导太阳轰炸技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Our destiny is with our homeland
Deadly melee killer, permanently invisible. Ability to use Blink, Sneak, and Guided Sun Bombing skills.

Can target the ground.

Name.zhCN: 折跃宗师圣堂武士

Tooltip.zhCN:
我们是卡拉之光
强大的灵能运用大师。能够使用审判、灵能风暴和灵能幻像技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
We are the Light of Kara
Powerful masters of psychic abilities. Ability to use Judgment, Psychic Storm, and Psychic Illusion skills.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
势不可挡
强大的灵能战士。可以使用潮涌灵能风暴和星界之风技能。

可以对地和对空。

Unstoppable

Tooltip.zhCN:
空中移动运输单位
可以装载或卸载单位，可变形为定点能量供给单位。能够使用浮游推进技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Aerial mobile transport unit
can load or unload units, and can be transformed into a fixed-point energy supply unit. Able to use floating propulsion skills.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
强大的战争机器
先进步战机器人，装备强大的范围攻击武器，可以攀越悬崖。能够使用灭绝指令技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Powerful war machine
 An advanced combat robot equipped with powerful range attack weapons that can climb cliffs. Ability to use the Extinction Command skill.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
先进范围伤害攻城部队。可以建造并发射圣甲虫，造成爆发性大范围伤害。能够使用部署甲虫骑士技能。

可以对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Advanced range damage to siege troops. Can build and launch Scarab, causing burst damage in a large area. Ability to use the Deploy Beetle Rider skill.

Can target the ground.
Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.

We will rise from the ashes

Can be used against ground and air.

诠释命运

Tooltip.enUS:
Interpretation of Destiny

Can target the ground.

命运的棱镜早已洞悉所有归途

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
The prism of fate has already seen all the way back
Advanced precision strike ship. Can be converted to orbital mode.

Can be used against ground and air.

家国恨, 今朝血

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Hate for family and country, blood today

Can be used against ground and air.

黄金舰队等待着

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
The golden fleet is waiting
to attack the city gunboat first. Can attack from very long distances.

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
出击时刻到了

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Time to attack

Can be used against ground and air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
为了艾尔的荣光

可以对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
For the Glory of Ayr
An advanced air superiority fighter capable of fighting large numbers of air units. Ability to use interference net skills.

Can be used against air.

Tooltip.zhCN:
我感受到了你的存在

可以对地和对空。
侦测单位
Tooltip.enUS:
I feel your presence

Can be used against ground and air.
Detection unit

可以对地和对空。

Our light will open a path across the galaxy
